Nutrient data for: CADBURY ROSES CHOCOLATE PIECES, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622210489876
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: MILK, sugar, glucose syrup, vegetable fats (palm, shea), cocoa butter, whey powder (from MILK), glucose-fructose syrup, cocoa mass, skimmed MILK powder, reduced fat cocoa powder, HAZELNUTS, emulsifiers (E442, SOYA lecithin, E471, sunflower lecithin, E476), rice flour, humectant (glycerol), salt, flavourings, sodium hydrogen carbonate, molasses, citric acid, whey protein concentrate (from MILK), sunflower oil, colours (anthocyanins, paprika extract). MILK CHOCOLATE: MILK SOLIDS 14% MINIMUM.MILK CHOCOLATE AND CHOCOLATE CONTAIN VEGETABLE FATS IN ADDITION TO COCOA BUTTER. MAY CONTAIN OTHER NUTS.
